Just incase you need a sign to know we going into 2023 happy. So get up, clean up, eat good and play some good music. Let’s be happy crossing over, let be grateful and graceful. 2022 took a lot so 2023 have to give it back. It owe all of us. Whether I know you personally or not I’m glad you made it here. So let’s make 2023 count and bring it in with a blast. Let’s make 2023 give us that promotion you been working for, that business you been trying to grow, that family you been trying to build, that investment, land, house, and car you been wanting. Peace, Love, and Happiness. Let’s show love to the ones we lost and live for them from here on out. Make sure you share the good vibes and live with your friends and family.

I used to enjoy entertaining y’all on this internet then I up and stopped. Well let me give y’all an update in my life for the last couple of year. 
Of course you all know I became a father to a beautiful baby girl. She struck something in me that made me say I had to go back and finish everything that I started. 

•So first I went to get my dealers license(2020), 

•then I went on to a bigger challenge to get my real estate license (2021). •

•After that I went on to get my CDL (2022). I didn’t have plans on using all these I only wanted to prove to myself I could do it but to also be able to show my daughter when she get older. I was just grateful God blessed me with the skills to get them. Now I think I want to challenge myself to use them all Say hello to you newest Ga realest agent / commercial driver/ car salesman😂😂. I don’t think I’m stopping here ether. Let’s work let’s create some partnerships and business together. Even if you just want to talk about them feel free to reach out to me.  To everyone who cheered me on during this journey I Thank and I love you.  #blessed #happy #hustle #hustlers #grind #girldad

Ever since I was young I always wanted to be 30. I always wanted to be unk. some people despise getting old but I love it because I’m getting seasoned, I’m getting wiser, I’m gaining more experience and it’s a blessing to be able to wake up everyday. I cherish that I made it because so many people didn’t make it this far. So when I celebrate my birthday it’s no only for me but for everyone who we lost along way. Y’all the reason I keep on living outside of my daughter. Unfortunately the list gets longer every year but I’ll never forget any one and I love you all. I really made it here I really made it 30 times around this sun so I’m always grateful for that. I made it to double OG triple OG status 😂😂. Im OG Big daddy now 😂😂. So to the first half of my life I thank you for the experiences, the journey, the people , the money , the careers and the fun I’ve had on along the way. Happy Money day to you old guy (Me) I love you more than ever keep growing, keep learning, keep inspiring, keep being inspired but most importantly keep on living. Make the second part of your life the best part of your life big fella. Chase your dreams harder, work at being the best man you can be. importantly be the man, most importantly the best dad you can be. Happy Solar eclipse big country.

To my 20’s Thank you for making me chase a dream that took me many places and introduce me to half the people I know now. had I not chased that dream majority of you wouldn’t know me. From y’all watch me chase cougars, to dancing in any place, to being everyone’s relatable uncle or grandpa to acting like the average gangsta however you met me we’ve all shared many laughs in my 20’s. This decade of my life was chasing my dreams was phenomenal. I can only imagine how hard we go in our 30’s. Let’s get it done and let’s get to work.

To my 20’s thank you for grinding to be able to travel the way you wanted. From riding jet skis in Bahamas to flipping off them in Saint Maarten. From eating seafood and dancing in the streets of New Orleans to dancing in to solo partying with the Haitians and UK people in Cancun. From solo tripping to Panama City Panama to flying back and forth to Jamaica just for authentic food. Riding around in old school cars in Cuba to random road trips just to go fishing in the Gulf. What about the random trips to Chicago and New York just to see who has the better pizza😂😂. Even going back and forth to the DR before the passport bros made it a thing. (Iykyk) 😂😂 To my twenties you did your thing with something you love but watch how we show you up in these 30’s. Let’s see where the adventures takes us this decade. Who traveling with me?

To my 20’s you gave me my most important gift/Title, you made me a father. You gave me my Big Mama, My Cookie Monster, my Baby girl, my feisty lady .  Over these last couple of years there has been a lot of teaching, growing, emotions and most importantly love. No other task has been more important than watching you grow my love bug I wouldn’t trade it for nothing in the world. You’ve shown me how to love like no other. You’ve shown me how to be emotional because the lord knows my heart on a my sleeves about you baby girl. I love you like no other. I can’t believe you’re already two. Where has the time gone. Please don’t grow up on me too fast. Happy birthday to my love. I can’t wait to get ice cream wasted with you today. 🖤💚🖤💚🖤💚🖤💚🖤
